{"tid":213587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土地遭暴力徵收越南農民封村挾警","createTime":"2017-04-23T08:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T08:35:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84bc736c8671174f4d8318e9de72cc068d2ac3f1","tid":213587,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170420/640_599665efe4350c2dec21757fbeeb421c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170420%2F640_599665efe4350c2dec21757fbeeb421c.jpg&h=f336fc87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南河內市美德縣近日有農民為抗議土地遭軍方旗下公司違法徵收，用沙包、磚塊等封村，阻止徵地，更挾持38名警員和官員作為人質，放話會抵抗任何救援行動，若當局採取強硬行動就會放火燒屋，把人質燒死。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，38名人質中有3人逃跑，15人獲釋，目前尚有20人被扣留在村內，但村民表示有提供食物及水給人質。當地政府稱，這塊土地本來屬於國防用途，過去借給村民使用耕作，現在要徵收；但村民認為現正處理事件的均為貪污官員，要求河內中央政府介入。上週六的衝突中，警方曾對天鳴槍，部份村民遭拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1635886/%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%AD%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%81%E6%94%B6%C2%B7%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%81%E6%9D%91%E6%8C%9F%E8%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinchew.com.my%2Fnode%2F1635886%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25BF%259D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%2581%25E6%2594%25B6%25C2%25B7%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%2586%259C%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%258C%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=741570d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1635886/%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%AD%E8%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%81%E6%94%B6%C2%B7%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%81%E6%9D%91%E6%8C%9F%E8%AD%A6</a>"}]}